{"data":[{"name":"79:1","price":"Juro por los [ángeles] que arrancan las almas [de los que desmienten el Mensaje],","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰزِعَٰتِ غَرۡقٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5713,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:2","price":"por los [ángeles] que toman suavemente las almas [de los creyentes],","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰشِطَٰتِ نَشۡطٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5714,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:3","price":"por los [ángeles] que viajan por el cosmos,","arabic":"وَٱلسَّٰبِحَٰتِ سَبۡحٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5715,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:4","price":"por los [ángeles] que se apresuran [a cumplir su función]","arabic":"فَٱلسَّٰبِقَٰتِ سَبۡقٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5716,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:5","price":"y por los [ángeles] que cumplen su mandato.","arabic":"فَٱلۡمُدَبِّرَٰتِ أَمۡرٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5717,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:6","price":"Que el día que sea tocada la trompeta por primera vez [y comience el fin del mundo]","arabic":"يَوۡمَ تَرۡجُفُ ٱلرَّاجِفَةُ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5718,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:7","price":"y luego sea tocada por segunda vez [y comience la resurrección],","arabic":"تَتۡبَعُهَا ٱلرَّادِفَةُ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5719,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:8","price":"los corazones se estremecerán","arabic":"قُلُوبٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ وَاجِفَةٌ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5720,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:9","price":"y las miradas estarán abatidas.","arabic":"أَبۡصَٰرُهَا خَٰشِعَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5721,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:10","price":"Pero a pesar de esto [los que desmienten el Mensaje] dicen: \"¿Acaso seremos resucitados de las tumbas","arabic":"يَقُولُونَ أَءِنَّا لَمَرۡدُودُونَ فِي ٱلۡحَافِرَةِ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5722,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:11","price":"a pesar de habernos convertido en polvo?\"","arabic":"أَءِذَا كُنَّا عِظَٰمٗا نَّخِرَةٗ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5723,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:12","price":"Dicen: \"Si sucediera, estaríamos arruinados\".","arabic":"قَالُواْ تِلۡكَ إِذٗا كَرَّةٌ خَاسِرَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5724,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:13","price":"Pero bastará que la trompeta sea tocada una vez","arabic":"فَإِنَّمَا هِيَ زَجۡرَةٞ وَٰحِدَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5725,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:14","price":"para que todos salgan de sus tumbas.","arabic":"فَإِذَا هُم بِٱلسَّاهِرَةِ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5726,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:15","price":"¿Acaso has escuchado la historia de Moisés?","arabic":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ مُوسَىٰٓ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5727,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:16","price":"Cuando su Señor lo llamó en el valle sagrado de Tuwa","arabic":"إِذۡ نَادَىٰهُ رَبُّهُۥ بِٱلۡوَادِ ٱلۡمُقَدَّسِ طُوًى","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5728,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"en el valle sagrado de Tuwa: Ver Corán 20:112. ","lang":"es"},{"name":"79:17","price":"[y le dijo:] \"Ve ante el Faraón, pues se ha excedido,","arabic":"ٱذۡهَبۡ إِلَىٰ فِرۡعَوۡنَ إِنَّهُۥ طَغَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5729,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:18","price":"y dile: ‘¿No deseas purificar tu comportamiento?","arabic":"فَقُلۡ هَل لَّكَ إِلَىٰٓ أَن تَزَكَّىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5730,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:19","price":"Yo te enseñaré el sendero de tu Señor para que seas piadoso’\".","arabic":"وَأَهۡدِيَكَ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَتَخۡشَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5731,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:20","price":"Y [Moisés] le mostró [al Faraón] uno de sus grandes milagros.","arabic":"فَأَرَىٰهُ ٱلۡأٓيَةَ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5732,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"Referencia a cuando Moisés arrojó su vara y esta se convirtió en serpiente, y cuando introdujo su mano cerca de su corazón y esta salió blanca, resplandeciente.","lang":"es"},{"name":"79:21","price":"Pero el Faraón lo desmintió y rechazó seguirlo.","arabic":"فَكَذَّبَ وَعَصَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5733,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:22","price":"Luego le dio la espalda y desobedeció [el Mensaje].","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَدۡبَرَ يَسۡعَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5734,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:23","price":"Y convocó [a su pueblo] y les dijo:","arabic":"فَحَشَرَ فَنَادَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5735,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:24","price":"\"Yo soy su Señor supremo\".","arabic":"فَقَالَ أَنَا۠ رَبُّكُمُ ٱلۡأَعۡلَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5736,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:25","price":"Por eso Dios lo castigará en la otra vida, pero también en esta.","arabic":"فَأَخَذَهُ ٱللَّهُ نَكَالَ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةِ وَٱلۡأُولَىٰٓ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5737,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:26","price":"En esta historia hay motivo de reflexión para quien tiene temor de Dios.","arabic":"إِنَّ فِي ذَٰلِكَ لَعِبۡرَةٗ لِّمَن يَخۡشَىٰٓ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5738,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:27","price":"¿Acaso piensan que ustedes fueron más difíciles de crear que el cielo que Él edificó?","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ أَشَدُّ خَلۡقًا أَمِ ٱلسَّمَآءُۚ بَنَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5739,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:28","price":"Él lo elevó y perfeccionó su construcción.","arabic":"رَفَعَ سَمۡكَهَا فَسَوَّىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5740,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:29","price":"Dios hizo que la noche fuese oscura y que le sucediera la claridad de la mañana.","arabic":"وَأَغۡطَشَ لَيۡلَهَا وَأَخۡرَجَ ضُحَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5741,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:30","price":"Luego extendió la tierra.","arabic":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضَ بَعۡدَ ذَٰلِكَ دَحَىٰهَآ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5742,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:31","price":"Hizo surgir de ella agua y pasturas.","arabic":"أَخۡرَجَ مِنۡهَا مَآءَهَا وَمَرۡعَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5743,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:32","price":"Fijó las montañas.","arabic":"وَٱلۡجِبَالَ أَرۡسَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5744,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:33","price":"Todo para beneficio de ustedes y de sus rebaños.","arabic":"مَتَٰعٗا لَّكُمۡ وَلِأَنۡعَٰمِكُمۡ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5745,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:34","price":"El día que suceda la gran calamidad [el fin del mundo]","arabic":"فَإِذَا جَآءَتِ ٱلطَّآمَّةُ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5746,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:35","price":"el ser humano recordará todo lo que haya hecho,","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَتَذَكَّرُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَا سَعَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5747,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:36","price":"y será expuesto el fuego del Infierno para que lo vean.","arabic":"وَبُرِّزَتِ ٱلۡجَحِيمُ لِمَن يَرَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5748,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:37","price":"Quien se haya extralimitado","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَن طَغَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5749,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:38","price":"y preferido la vida mundanal,","arabic":"وَءَاثَرَ ٱلۡحَيَوٰةَ ٱلدُّنۡيَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5750,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:39","price":"su morada será el Infierno.","arabic":"فَإِنَّ ٱلۡجَحِيمَ هِيَ ٱلۡمَأۡوَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5751,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:40","price":"En cambio, quien haya tenido conciencia de que comparecerá ante su Señor y haya preservado su alma de seguir sus pasiones,","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ خَافَ مَقَامَ رَبِّهِۦ وَنَهَى ٱلنَّفۡسَ عَنِ ٱلۡهَوَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5752,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:41","price":"su morada será el Paraíso.","arabic":"فَإِنَّ ٱلۡجَنَّةَ هِيَ ٱلۡمَأۡوَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5753,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:42","price":"Te preguntan cuándo será la hora del Juicio Final.","arabic":"يَسۡـَٔلُونَكَ عَنِ ٱلسَّاعَةِ أَيَّانَ مُرۡسَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5754,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:43","price":"Pero tú [¡oh, Mujámmad!] no tienes conocimiento de cuándo será.","arabic":"فِيمَ أَنتَ مِن ذِكۡرَىٰهَآ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5755,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:44","price":"Solo tu Señor lo sabe.","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ مُنتَهَىٰهَآ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5756,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:45","price":"Tú solamente eres un advertidor para quienes tienen temor [al Juicio].","arabic":"إِنَّمَآ أَنتَ مُنذِرُ مَن يَخۡشَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5757,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"es"},{"name":"79:46","price":"El día que lo vean suceder, les parecerá haber permanecido en la vida mundanal solo el tiempo equivalente a una tarde o una mañana.","arabic":"كَأَنَّهُمۡ يَوۡمَ يَرَوۡنَهَا لَمۡ يَلۡبَثُوٓاْ إِلَّا عَشِيَّةً أَوۡ ضُحَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5758,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"Como en muchos otros lugares del Corán (2:259, 17:52, 18:19, 20:103-104, 23:112-113, 30:55, etc.), esto es una indicación sutil de la naturaleza terrenal e ilusoria del concepto humano de “tiempo”, un concepto que perderá todo significado en el contexto de la realidad última comprendida en el término “más allá” (Al Ájira).","lang":"es"}],"chapter":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at","Chapter An-Nazi'at","Nazi'at","Surah Nazi'at","Chapter Nazi'at","An Nazi'at","Surah An Nazi'at","Chapter An Nazi'at","Surah 79","Chapter 79","Those Who Pull Out","النازعات"]}